condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part A Paragraph 3 | Description :The Borrower, through the MOJ, shallmaintain the Steering Committee, at all times during Project implementation , with a composition, resources & terms of referencesatisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part B Paragraph 2 | Description :The Borrower shall...cause the MOJ...toinclude adequate allocations in...respective budgets for (i) O&M for ICT systems developed under the project & (ii) ICT...trainingfor relevant staff. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part B Paragraph 3 | Description :(f) For..Parts A.1 and B.1 of theProject, the Borrower..shall ensure that buildings..where construction..are undertaken..are adequately maintained & provideadequate access for the disabled. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part B Paragraph 4(a) | Description :The Borrower shall cause MOJ & theSteering Committee to hold semi-annual consultations with...stakeholders including...the Bar Associations, association of notaries,civil society...media.. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part B Paragraph 4(b) | Description :The Borrower shall cause MOJ, theSupreme Court, the SAO, SAO offices & courts...to publish, on their...public website..annual..information [on]implementation...ICMS & CTS performance data... | Frequency :Annually

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part B Paragraph 4(c) | Description :The Borrower shall cause MOJ to design& develop, within 24 months following the Effectiveness Date, a medium-term expenditure framework for the justicesector..satisfactory to the Bank... | Due Date :11-Jul-2012

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement Schedule 2 Section I Part D Paragraph 1(a) | Description :The Borrower, through the Ministry ofJustice, shall (i) shall duly perform all obligations under the Environmental Management Plans in a timely manner... | Frequency:Yearly
